GoldenEye::
She smiled and hugged Dollen. She put her finger to her lips."Shhh, 
love.  KitKat is busy, and I'm trying to pay attention."  She kissed 
him and hugged him. "But it's great to see you again."

::KitKat::
She turned and looked at Dollen and GoldenEye."You two may go inside. 
GoldenEye, see that your friend has  quarters and is settled in. I 
will see to these two bots and then return to my other meeting."

GoldenEye::
She smiled. "Yes KitKat." She took Dollen's arm and walked inside the 
base.

DarkMouse::
She looked at GoldenEye and Dollen. She smiled, remembering when she 
was like that with a bot. The smile left her face as she remembered 
how he left her.



--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "dcoburn" <dcoburn@n...> wrote:
> ::Dollen::
> 
>          After a while, Dollen finally got to the base where 
everybody was.
> 
>           "Yes, I'm back," He said, running up to the base.
> 
>          Dollen ran into the room where GoldenEye, DarkMouse, Koj, 
KitKat and Inu-Yusha were faster than you could say get a spark.
> 
>           He looked at GoldenEye.
> 
>           "Hey love, how are ya??  How 'bout introducing me to your 
friends?" He said.
